Interface Summary
MonitorableTask Classes that perform long tasks (like graph algorithms) can implement this interface so that they can be monitored by a GUI like a javax.swing.plaf.ProgressBarUI or a javax.swing.ProgressMonitor Note: this was copied from giny.util because it is being phased out.

Package csplugins.mcode Description

Cytoscape PlugIn that clusters a network. Can be used to detect complexes in a molecular interaction network.
